title: THURSDAY 3/4 - Quarterbacks on the move?
itunes:title: THURSDAY 3/4 - Quarterbacks on the move?
description:
Baker Mayfield fresh off a playoff appearance this season and General Manager Andrew Berry things will only get better for Baker and the Browns (0:07). Derek Carr's name has been tossed around in trade rumors, but Mike Mayock standing by his QB (1:23). The same goes for Kirk Cousins in Minnesota (2:25), but the future of Sam Darnold (2:38) not as stable
